title: EPA Fuel Economy Products Testing
description:
Collection of EPA documents covering various products over the years touting to boost fuel economy and/or reduce various exhaust gas emissions.

EPA tested them and/or gave their reasons why the ideas behind them were wrong or made sense.

The same files are freely available directly through the EPA's website, but the PDFs are not named usefully nor are they in one collection like this.

Contains the following 93 documents in PDF format.

Enjoy. :)
